    <body>
      <div type="edition" xml:id="edition-text" xml:space="preserve">
        <head>Edition</head>
        <div type="section" subtype="part">
          <div type="section" subtype="case" n="C.4">
            <head>(C.4)</head>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 d.init.">
              <head>(C.4 d.init.)</head>
              <ab>
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">Quidam</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P"/>
                </app>
                in
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">excommunicatione</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">excomunicatione</rdg>
                </app>
                constitutus episcopum accusare disponit;
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">adolescentem</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">adulescentem</rdg>
                </app>
                infra xiiiium
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Bc #P">etatis sue annum</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Aa">annum etatis sue</rdg>
                </app>
                ad assertionem sue cause adducit. Prohibitus ab accusatione
                adolescentem accusatorem et se testem facit. Adolescens personam
                accusatoris et testis gerere cupit;
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">die</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">di</rdg>
                </app>
                statuta ad
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicium</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditium</rdg>
                </app>
                electorum
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">iudicum</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">iudicium</rdg>
                </app>
                episcopus minime
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">concurrit</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr.">occurrit</rdg>
                </app>;
                a communione
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">suspenditur</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">suspendere</rdg>
                </app>;
                tandem renouato
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                </app>
                accusator culpabilis in accusatione
                inuenitur; demum ad assertionem proprie cause procedit. Hic primum
                queritur, an in excommunicatione constitutus alium accusare ualeat?
                Secundo,
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">an</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">autem</rdg>
                </app>
                infra
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc"/>
                  <rdg wit="#P">infra</rdg>
                </app>
                xiiiium annum in
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">criminali</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">criminari</rdg>
                </app>
                causa testari quis possit? Tercio, utrum
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ab</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P"/>
                </app>
                accusatione prohibitus personam testificantis possit assumere?
                Quarto,
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">an idem possit esse accusator et testis? Quinto,</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P"/>
                </app>
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">an</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">aut</rdg>
                </app>
                die constituta non occurrens a communione sit remouendus? Sexto, si
                in episcoporum
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                </app>
                accusatoris persona culpabilis inuenta
                fuerit, an ad assertionem proprie cause de cetero sit admittenda?
              </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="section" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.1">
              <head>(C.4 q.1)</head>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.1 d.a.c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.1 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab>
                  De prima questione sic statutum legitur in
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Aa #P">concilio</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Bc">comcilio</rdg>
                  </app>
                  Cartaginensi .vii. cui interfuit Faustinus Romane ecclesie legatus:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.1 c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.1 c.1)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <ab>
                    Ad accusandum non
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">admittitur</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">admittatur</rdg>
                    </app>
                    qui in excommunicatione perseuerat.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Diffinimus, eum rite ad accusationem non admitti, qui
                    posteaquam excommunicatus
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">fuerit</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">fuit</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    in ipsa adhuc excommunicatione constitutus, siue sit
                    clericus
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">siue laicus</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>,
                    accusare uoluerit. Omnes etiam infamie maculis aspersi, id
                    est
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">istriones</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">hystriones</rdg>
                    </app>
                    aut turpitudinibus subiecte persone, heretici etiam, siue
                    pagani siue Iudei, ab accusatione prohibentur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div type="section" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.2-3">
              <head>(C.4 q.2-3)</head>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.2-3 d.a.c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.2-3 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab>
                  Secunda autem et tercia questio eodem concilio, uno eodemque capitulo
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Bc #P">terminatur</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Aa">terminatur</rdg>
                  </app>.
                  Illud uero est huiusmodi:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.2-3 c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.2-3 c.1)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <ab>
                    Qui ab accusatione repelluntur,
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#P">aut</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">et</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc"/>
                    </app>
                    ad annum .xiiii. nondum peruenerunt, testes esse non possunt.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Testes autem ad testimonium
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">non</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">admittendos</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">admttendos</rdg>
                    </app>
                    censemus, qui nec ad accusationem admitti iussi sunt, uel
                    etiam quos ipse accusator de domo sua produxerit. Ad
                    testimonium autem
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">intra</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">infra</rdg>
                    </app>
                    annos .xiiii. etatis sue constituti non admittantur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.2-3 d.p.c.3">
                  <head>(C.4 q.2-3 d.p.c.3)</head>
                  <!-- "Set" or "Sed"? -->
                  <ab>
                    Set obicitur illud beati
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">Bricii</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">Brichi</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    qui uoce pueri .xxx. dies ab
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ortu</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">hortu</rdg>
                    </app>
                    habentis innocens probatus est. Set miracula diuina sunt
                    admiranda, non in exemplum humane
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">actionis</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">accionis</rdg>
                    </app>
                    trahenda.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div type="section" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.4">
              <head>(C.4 q.4)</head>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.4 d.a.c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.4 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab>
                  De
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Bc #P">quarta</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Aa">.iiii.</rdg>
                  </app>
                  uero questione Fabianus papa constituit, dicens:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.4 c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.4 c.1)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <ab>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">Accusator, testis uel iudex aliquis simul esse non potest.</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">Quilibet duas personas in causa <sic>gegrere</sic> non ualet.</rdg>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Nullus umquam presumat accusator simul esse et iudex uel testis, quoniam in omni
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem>quatuor</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">iiii</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iiii<add place="above">o</add></rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#P">iiii<add place="above">or</add></rdg>
                    </app> personas semper
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">necesse est esse</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr.">esse necesse est</rdg>
                    </app>, id
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">est</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    iudices electos, et
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">accusatores</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa"><add place="above">idoneos</add>accusatores</rdg>
                    </app>, ac
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">defensores</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">defensores<add place="above">congruos</add></rdg>
                    </app> atque
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">testes</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa"><add place="above">legitimos</add>testes</rdg>
                    </app>.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.4 c.2">
                <head>(C.4 q.4 c.2)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="inscription">
                  <ab>Item Damasus papa.</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <ab>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">Quilibet in causa duas personas gerere non ualet.</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">Accusator, testis uel iudex aliquis simul esse non potest.</rdg>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Nullus introducatur personaliter
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ad causam</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">adusam</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    <!-- "sed" or "set"? ſ; in Aa and P, ſ⁊ in Bc. -->
                    set accusatores et accusati equa audiantur ratione, iuxta
                    quod ordo exigit. Accusatores uero et iudices non idem sint,
                    set
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">per se accusatores,</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    per se iudices, per se testes, per se accusati, unusquisque
                    in suo ordine. Inscriptio
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P"/>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">uero</rdg>
                    </app>
                    semper fiat ut
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">talionem calumpniator</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">calumpniator talionem</rdg>
                    </app>
                    recipiat, quia ante inscriptionem nemo debet iudicari uel
                    dampnari, cum et seculi leges hec eadem retineant.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div type="section" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.5">
              <head>(C.4 q.5)</head>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.5 d.a.c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.5 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab>
                  De .v. uero questione in concilio cartaginensi
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Bc">tertio</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Aa">.iii.</rdg>
                    <rdg wit="#P">tercio</rdg>
                  </app>
                  sic
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">inuenitur</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#P"><sic>inueuenitur</sic></rdg>
                  </app>
                  diffinitum.
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.5 c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.5 c.1)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <ab>
                    Non est a communione suspendendus, qui die statuta ad causam
                    peruenire non potuit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Quisquis episcoporum accusatur, ad primates
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">prouincie</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">prouintie</rdg>
                    </app>
                    ipsius causam deferat accusator. Nec a communione
                    suspendatur cui crimen intenditur, nisi ad causam suam
                    dicendam electorum
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">iudicum</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">iudicium</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    die statuta,
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">litteris</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">litteras</rdg>
                    </app>
                    euocatus minime occurrerit, hoc est
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc">infra spatium</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">intra spacium</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#P">infra infra spatium</rdg>
                    </app>
                    mensis ex ea die, qua eum litteras accepisse constiterit.
                    Quod si aliquas ueras necessitatis causas
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">probauerit</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">propriauerit</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    quibus occurrere non potuisse manifestum sit, cause sue
                    dicende intra alterum mensem integram habeat facultatem.
                    Verum tamdiu post mensem secundum non communicet, donec
                    purgetur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div type="section" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.6">
              <head>(C.4 q.6)</head>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.6 d.a.c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab>
                  Sexta uero questio eodem capitulo terminatur, in quo sequitur:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.1">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.1)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <!-- R2: "In ciuili et proprio dumtaxat negotio ad arguendum
                  admittitur, qui in episcopi accusatione culpabilis inuenitur." -->
                  <ab>
                    Qui in accusatione episcopi culpabilis inuenitur ad
                    arguendum de cetero non admittatur nisi propriam causam
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ciuilem</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    solummodo asserere uoluerit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Illud uero placuit, ut cum agere ceperit in episcoporum
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    si fuerit
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">accusatoris</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">accusator</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa">persona</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc #P"/>
                    </app>
                    dampnabilis de cetero ad arguendum non admittatur, nisi
                    proprias causas, non tamen ecclesiasticas uel criminales,
                    asserere uoluerit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.2">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.2)</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="inscription">
                  <ab>
                    Item ex
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">concilio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">comcilio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">cartaginensi</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">cartaginesi</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">.vii.</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">.viio.</rdg>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <!-- R2: "Propriam causam agere ualet cui accusare non licet." -->
                  <!-- spelling: "audientia" or "audiencia"? -->
                  <ab>
                    Non
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">negatur</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">negant</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">audientia in</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">in audientia</rdg>
                    </app>
                    propria causa
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">cuius</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">cui</rdg>
                    </app>
                    accusatio interdicitur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Omnibus quibus accusatio denegatur in causis propriis
                    accusandi licentia
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">non est</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">est non</rdg>
                    </app>
                    neganda.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.3">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.3 [Bc only])</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="inscription">
                  <ab>Item Felix episcopus omnibus episcopis</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="rubric">
                  <ab>
                    In episcoporum accusatione
                    <app>
                      <lem>deficiens</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">defitiens</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    ciuiliter
                    <app>
                      <lem>tantum</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">tatum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    experiri poterit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Si accusatorum persone in
                    <app>
                      <lem>iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    episcoporum culpabiles
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc">apparuerint</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr."><sic>aparuerint</sic></rdg>
                    </app>,
                    ad arguendum non admittantur, nisi proprias causas asserere,
                    non tamen criminales uel ecclesiasticas, uoluerint.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div type="section" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.4">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.4 [Bc only])</head>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="inscription">
                  <ab>Item Adrianus papa</ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="canon">
                  <ab>
                    Quod si accusatorum persone in
                    <app>
                      <lem>iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    episcoporum et cetera, ut supra eisdem uerbis.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
